The Tecno Pop 5C joins the league of Tecno Pop 5P, which was launched in the market in August last year. The smartphone has been launched in the global market, the company did not reveal the pricing of the smartphone. However, it has gone official on its global website. The smartphone has been offered in two colour options including Lake Blue and Dark Blue. If launched in India, the smartphone may cost somewhere between Rs 3000 to Rs 5000.